Source: sky1-vpu-dkms
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/Sky1-Linux/sky1-drivers-dkms

Package: sky1-vpu-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Description: CIX Sky1 Video Processing Unit driver (DKMS)
 This package provides the AMVX driver for the CIX Sky1 VPU using DKMS.
 .
 Hardware: ARM Technology China Linlon MVE (Mali Video Engine) v8
 with 5 AEU cores providing V4L2 stateful video encoding/decoding.
 .
 Supported codecs: H.264, HEVC, VP8, VP9, AV1, MPEG-2/4, VC-1, AVS/AVS2, JPEG
